late-night television, and NBC found that

00:00:18.410 --> 00:00:22.730
out a few months ago when Conan O'Brien,
the newly installed host of The Tonight

00:00:22.730 --> 00:00:27.380
Show, quit after the network announced it
was going to push the Tonight Show into

00:00:27.380 --> 00:00:32.029
tomorrow, and to give its traditional
timeslot back to O'Brien's predecessor

00:00:32.029 --> 00:00:37.310
Jay Leno. It triggered a lot of bad
publicity for NBC, an outpouring of

00:00:37.310 --> 00:00:41.480
public support for Conan and some of the
best late-night jokes in a decade.

00:00:41.480 --> 00:00:46.130
Conan walked away with a 32 million
dollar settlement and a new cable show,

00:00:46.130 --> 00:00:51.050
