oblivion, legally prohibiting him from

00:00:51.050 --> 00:00:55.219
saying anything false or disparaging
about the network, and from giving

00:00:55.219 --> 00:01:00.829
interviews or appearing on television
until...now. If you're wondering what

00:01:00.829 --> 00:01:05.860
happened to Conan O'Brien and what he
thinks about all of this, you're about to find out.

00:01:05.860 --> 00:01:08.600
